freeFloat().details: Remember, totalFloat returns ALL shares supply, even if underlying is locked outside of Vault.

earn().notice: Transfer any available and not limited by cap funds to Controller (=>Strategy).

idleFloat().notice: Idle funds in Vault, i.e deposits before earn()
